Package database

Class Database

java.lang.Object
database.Database
public class Database extends Object
The Database class holds static lists that store instances of various entities in the application, including applicants, managers, officers, projects, enquiries, flat bookings, and application history. This class serves as a central repository for managing and accessing all core data objects in the application.
